RE QuotesPST jon i had no s yesterday because andy was out and adam left us to return to london for good hence no northeast markets we are helping the canadian office each day and andys back today at the end of the day ill fill out as much as possible john Original Message From Mckay Jonathan SMTPJonathan NRONcom Sent Monday December PM To Mckay Brad Brawner Sandra F Subject Quotes Thank you very much for your work so far gathering market data In an effort to consolidate our requests I have started to include the gulf coast market points This should help limit our random inquiries about different locations and allow everyone to focus on their current business responsibilities Your continued help each night is still needed in verifying the markets during our restructuring time Thank
